{"tid":1261160,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"629齊齊參與解放軍碼頭開幕","createTime":"2019-06-27T06:02:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-29T03:02:08.000Z","uid":90306,"like":98,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"71f5b5bfe7b4bd86b3e10a59a7c39277b3d97970","tid":1261160,"uid":90306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T06:02:33.000Z","msg":"照道理個五條附屬法例就會自動生效，而根據政府所講，到時解放軍會於一般時間開放附近海濱長廊予公眾使用。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">為咗一睹軍用碼頭嘅風采，誠邀各位6月29日朝早11點去幫解放軍開幕！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">明明開放公眾使用，6月29日一於幫佢開閘做第一批訪客。<br />\n<br />\n海旁咁靚，但係碼頭圍住咗幾年生到成地雜草，一於入去幫香港嘅海濱除習總，sorry除雜草。<br />\n<br />\n除完雜草當然係坐低欣賞維多利亞港啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/waterfront2_QAXjz_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fwaterfront2_QAXjz_1200x0.png&h=44fe8a73&s={SIZE}\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">！！碼頭建築係禁區千萬唔好入！！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">至於喺外面坐解放軍未請保安理論上都唔會有問題（求法律JJ解答）</span><br />\n<br />\n</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">根據《受保護地方(保安)條例》(第 260 章)第 2 條作出<br />\r\n《2019 年受保護地方(修訂)令》(見附件 A)，藉以把<br />\r\n碼頭<ins>陸上範圍列為「受保護地方」；</ins><br />\r\n(b) 根據《受保護地方(保安)條例》(第 260 章)第 3 條作出<br />\r\n《2019 年受保護地方(保安)(特派守衞)(修訂)令》(見<br />\r\n附件 B)，藉以授權中國人民解放軍駐港部隊(簡稱「駐<br />\r\n軍」)聘用的公司所僱用的<ins>合資格守衞人員作為碼頭的<br />\r\n「特派守衞」</ins>；<br />\r\n(c) 根據《公安條例》(第 245 章)第 36(1)條作出《2019 年<br />\r\n軍事設施禁區(修訂)令》(見附件 C)，藉以把<ins>碼頭範圍<br />\r\n內的四座建築物列為「禁區」；</ins>以及</span><br />\n<br />\nCap260-8 任何人如 &mdash;&mdash;<br />\n(a)在受到特派守衞盤問時沒有止步；<br />\n(b)抗拒或妨礙特派守衞履行本條例委予他的職責或行使本條例賦予他的權力，或協助或煽惑任何人抗拒或妨礙特派守衞履行本條例委予他的職責或行使本條例賦予他的權力；<br />\n(c)(由1997年第1號第27條廢除)<br />\n(d)未獲授權而進入受保護地方，並在特派守衞或警隊人員要求他離開該地方的緊接範圍時沒有離開，<br />\n即屬犯罪，一經循簡易程序定罪，可處第1級罰款及監禁6個月。"},{"pid":"6b49f1ec818aba2d3d97e8049ff9d8bb8d069c63","tid":1261160,"uid":90306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T06:03:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"309600dd3d7d39ba32b252b706dd27fdce7dcee7","tid":1261160,"uid":48667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T06:05:16.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"077dd64c3f3d6399421834ca16fc59c3310c8c31","tid":1261160,"uid":55628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T06:05:55.000Z","msg":"推到上宇宙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c4d14d1e6504b6cbe251e9de90d731a872b0d8d","tid":1261160,"uid":90306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T06:07:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"270eaa6c4b3d8030a66f4a8aa9003ac5837f3f00","tid":1261160,"uid":90306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T06:10:35.000Z","msg":"真心求法律JJ解下有無錯"},{"pid":"ddcd9f12e00da44b28cdf8fbf6004bdfa9e9a656","tid":1261160,"uid":152147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T06:13:34.000Z","msg":"推爆佢"},{"pid":"4d843cbfccbff9a37f6671306a4eed20f215531c","tid":1261160,"uid":90306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T06:15:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d83d95957ec168894fe773999c558bf127dd24f3","tid":1261160,"uid":90306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T06:20:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abb0e439722086510c235735256d864620cfd781","tid":1261160,"uid":106326,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T06:22:10.000Z","msg":"佢唔會一通過就開始動工改造架嘛⋯⋯<br />\n一塊無人既爛地你依家去有乜用⋯"},{"pid":"bbf50ba3aa728857827cc56a3cd15c8847be