 />\n昨、今（26至27日）兩日共16小時會議，有50多名議員發言，當中以建制派為主。今晚休會動議表決後，已屆會議完結時間，民主派即席提出明日（28日）加開會議討論廢例決議案，但被立法會主席梁君彥拒絕。民主派會後批評，建制派以至梁君彥是侮辱立法會的議事功能。<br />\n<br />\n政府透過5條附屬法例，將中環海濱一幅0.3公頃土地撥歸(偽)解放軍作(偽)軍用碼頭，民主派原本希望在立法會提出決議案，要求廢除相關附屬法例。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T15:30:31.000Z","msg":"聽日就G20，聽晚煲底見！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1262072\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1262072</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b276a25a741d97a179ce066b746c1f31c7e3aed4","tid":1261160,"uid":209225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8076263b6c5748a328f6d3c048e4188b493b55ba","tid":1261160,"uid":267600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T15:23:30.000Z","msg":"這可能會有危險，更要預防有鬼。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T15:30:48.000Z","msg":"聽日就G20，聽晚煲底見！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1262072\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1262072</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"fd2356491329ff8b503697d54ab2d1200633a002","tid":1261160,"uid":45206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"959f62ed6d45834f7c6eef9ab3f6a73c1a07d6e3","tid":1261160,"uid":209225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"64fa688a30637d1705d1d30004c643a3a23ee300","tid":1261160,"uid":45206,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T14:24:28.000Z","msg":"係就去西環表達不满 去個空嘅碼頭又9坐"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T15:30:07.000Z","msg":"聽日就G20，聽晚煲底見！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1262072\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1262072</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T15:32:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a2f114d654c4416386c601d67d8714c89eddb6d","tid":1261160,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T15:32:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" clas